Title: An Act Changing the Name of Butulan Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Romulo Factura Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 750
An Act Changing the Name of Butulan Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Romulo Factura Elementary School
Section 1. The name of Butulan Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao del Sur, is changed to Romulo Factura Elementary School.1awphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
